rows.label: tlk45320651_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I'd heard rumors about artificial Blades,
but I never thought someone had made
them a reality already...

rows.label: tlk45320651_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Our R&D team must be lagging behind.
Whoever developed that thing is
running rings around them.

rows.label: tlk45320651_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I guess there's something to be said for
Nopon innovation. Do you think any of
them would be willing to give a lecture?
